```plantuml
@startuml IBM_logdna-cos
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam arrowColor black
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "IBM Cloud Object Storage" as COS
actor "IBM LogDNA" as LogDNA

rectangle "Serverless Function (handler.js)" as Serverless {
    rectangle "COS Client" as COSClient
    rectangle "LogDNA Client" as LogDNAClient
    rectangle "Log Processing" as LogProcessing
    rectangle "Error Handling" as ErrorHandling
}

COS --> Serverless : Trigger on\nNew Object
Serverless --> COSClient : Download Log File
COSClient --> LogProcessing : Unzip & Parse JSON
LogProcessing --> LogDNAClient : Send Logs in Batches
LogDNAClient --> LogDNA : Forward Logs
LogProcessing --> COSClient : Archive & Delete\nProcessed Logs
LogProcessing --> ErrorHandling : Log & Retry on Failure

@enduml
```